## ðŸ“˜ **CELL 5 â€” FASTQC & Quality Control (Markdown)**

```markdown
# ðŸ”Ž Step 1: Quality Check of FASTQ Files

We begin by checking the quality of raw FASTQ files using **FastQC**.

This generates HTML reports showing:
